- normal: ordinary conversation, private knowledge lookup, and lightweight web work with the shared basic tools first
- documents: local files, folders, workspace analysis, document writing, report generation, then document-specific tools when the shared basic tools are not enough
- research: deep research, source tracking, evidence-heavy analysis, research-style reports, and the research_grounding skill layered on top of the shared basic tools
